danger lights is a 1930 american pre-code drama film directed by frank lloyd and starring frank morgan , jean arthur , george g. seitz and george g. kaufman . the film stars frank albertson , jean arthur , lionel barrymore , jean arthur , lionel barrymore , jean arthur , lionel barrymore , jean arthur , george g. kaufman and lionel barrymore . the film was released in the united states on june 17 , 1930 , by universal pictures .